document_data.name: Jaylee Clammath
document_data.refs3e: {{Cite web/Elminster Speaks archive|28}}{{Cite web/Elminster Speaks/Part 23: Cheap and Cheerful at the Three Elves}}
document_data.mainbody:
'''Jaylee Clammath''' was part-owner, cook, and hostess at the [[Three Elves]] inn in [[Voonlar]] ''circa'' the [[1372 DR|Year of Wild Magic, 1372 DR]].
__NOTOC__
document_data.Description: She was tall and quite overweight.
document_data.Personality: Jaylee was a cheerful person who liked to joke and laugh.
document_data.Relationships: The Three Elves was a very popular inn throughout the Moonsea region and its owner/operators were highly regarded.
